{"tid":2082762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[靜默遊行]港豬心聲：我都係想放假有得行街啫 你哋放過我啦好冇","createTime":"2020-06-28T09:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T10:54:06.000Z","uid":254426,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d311e3e3dee84eefb475ea031c1f5b360672130","tid":2082762,"uid":254426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"隱形遊行風險相對較低 但最大嘅缺點就係冇得表態畫面唔夠靚 所以遊行嘅重點應該<span style=\"color: red;\">以攬炒藍絲港豬為目標</span> 因為班狗暫時可以做嘅就係拉封鎖線然後ss 一個唔覺意就會截埋隻港豬 同埋封咗間藍店嘅門口 對家嘅損失分分鐘大過我哋 但前提係手足真係要冇裝喺身 就算畀人ss都唔驚有事<br />\n之後可以考慮每個禮拜喺唔同區騎劫各大行人路 除咗係多人行街嘅地方 仲可以揀啲多藍絲廢老嘅區 逼啲狗罰企之餘 順便幫一眾藍絲港豬親身體驗黑警嘅惡行 真正將抗爭融入生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c42d0b87e60ae3a43c7a941f40419fdae463d4","tid":2082762,"uid":254426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WT1tC4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WT1tC4.png&h=c06d30e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港豬心聲示意圖"},{"pid":"5a2098c107835b782208c2e93d519be0dabf8478","tid":2082762,"uid":254426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c42d0b87e60ae3a43c7a941f40419fdae463d4","tid":2082762,"uid":254426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WT1tC4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WT1tC4.png&h=c06d30e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港豬心聲示意圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbb6f15fe252007d7899d467d5d5c0d45d4c79f","tid":2082762,"uid":174676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"Sor hi錯負皮<br />\n想比